owth stocks of smallcap midcap and largecap companies to make its equity investments for its fixed income investments it invests in corporate debt securities commercial paper certificates of deposit united states government securities intermediateterm and longterm fixed income securities and municipal securities the firm employs a combination of fundamental thematic technical and quantitative analysis while making its investments it also uses a combination of a topdown and a bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolios the firm benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the spbarra growth index sp  index spbarra mid cap  growth index and russell  growth index it benchmarks the performance of its fixed income portfolios against the barclays capital intermediate governmentcredit index and barclays capital aggregate index the firm benchmarks the performance of its enhanced cash portfolios against the imoney net first tier institutional index merrill lynch  year treasury index and merrill lynch  year governmentscorp index it conducts inhouse research to make its investments the firm was founded in june  and is based in baltimore maryland with additional offices in washington district of columbia harrisburg pennsylvania new york new york hanover pennsylvania buffalo new york rochester new york state college pennsylvania and horsham pennsylvania mtb investment advisors inc operates as a subsidiary of mt bank inc detailed description  south calvert streetth floorbaltimore md united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwmtbiacom key executives for wilmington trust investment advisors inc mr jeffrey willis durkee chief executive officer age  mr karen purzitsky cfa vice president and senior quantitative research analyst mr michael dennis daniels cpa chief operating officer age  dr robert thomas sweet phd managing director of economics age  mr brett allen hoffacker cfp managing director age  compensation as of fiscal year  wilmington trust investment ad